## App Navigation Integration

The main app ([BankManagementSystemApp.java](file:///c:/Users/Youssef/Documents/Uni/Software/Semester%201/Project/Implementation/JavaApplication6/src/main/java/com/bms/BankManagementSystemApp.java)) currently only navigates to 4 screens and shows placeholder alerts for Deposit/Withdraw/Transfer. Each new use case needs:

1. A `show<ScreenName>()` method added to [BankManagementSystemApp](file:///c:/Users/Youssef/Documents/Uni/Software/Semester%201/Project/Implementation/JavaApplication6/src/main/java/com/bms/BankManagementSystemApp.java#22-213)
2. A menu item wired to that method in [createMenuBar()](file:///c:/Users/Youssef/Documents/Uni/Software/Semester%201/Project/Implementation/JavaApplication6/src/main/java/com/bms/BankManagementSystemApp.java#132-181)
3. The screen initialized in [start()](file:///c:/Users/Youssef/Documents/Uni/Software/Semester%201/Project/Implementation/JavaApplication6/src/main/java/com/bms/BankManagementSystemApp.java#30-66) and reset in [resetAll()](file:///c:/Users/Youssef/Documents/Uni/Software/Semester%201/Project/Implementation/JavaApplication6/src/main/java/com/bms/BankManagementSystemApp.java#121-131)
